RelatedSentence: Azerbaijan and Brazil will sign intergovernmental agreement on cooperation in customs sphere , said the chairman of State Custom Committee Aydin Aliyev at the meeting with Ernani Argolo Checcucci Filho , Undersecretary of the Customs and International Relations at Brazil 's Federal Revenue Service .

Azerbaijan and Brazil will sign intergovernmental agreement on cooperation in customs sphere , said the chairman of State Custom Committee Aydin Aliyev at the meeting with Ernani Argolo Checcucci Filho , Undersecretary of the Customs and International Relations at Brazil 's Federal Revenue Service .
